## ğŸ“‹ Common Commands

### Scenario Management
```bash
# List available scenarios
vrooli scenario list

# Get help for a specific scenario  
vrooli scenario help <scenario-name>

# Run a scenario
vrooli scenario run <scenario-name>

# Stop a running scenario
vrooli scenario stop <scenario-name>
```

### Development Workflow
```bash
