## ğŸš¨ Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**Scenario won't start**:
```bash
# Check resource status
vrooli status --resources

# Restart resources
vrooli setup --resources
```

**Performance issues**:
```bash
# Check resource usage
vrooli resource status --memory

# Stop unused scenarios
vrooli scenario stop --all
```

**Integration problems**:
```bash
# Verify integration health
vrooli-bridge status --project "{{project_name}}"

# Re-integrate if needed
vrooli-bridge integrate "{{project_path}}" --force
```

